e probably better off with a tink bag from SolA (about5-6k) then trying to buy a Leatherfoot one from a halfling tailor <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/ubackster.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Backster</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Contributing Member</span><br>  Posts: 261<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(8/21/02 12:51:47 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm25.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=58.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Leatherfoot Bags</span><hr size=1> Takes 4 Blue Diamonds for the big one just for an estimate.  I know Cuin from our guild is a halfing tailor and just hit about 221 - might want to hold onto your BDs as he's still working it up - and with geerlock or trophy should be capped soon.  Send him a tell if you're still interested or I can point him to here for you.<br>
